short_description: prestar packaging inc. is a paper & cardboard products supplier based in christiansburg, virginia, united states.
long_description: environmentally friendly 100% recyclable and made from post-consumer paper products. custom printing, foil stamping, and design services to give your packaging that extra personal touch. prestar packaging is a family owned manufacturing company located in christiansburg, virginia, specializing in all types of rigid set up boxes and folding boxes. we are a broad range facility, meaning we have the capability of producing small quantities as well as large run projects. learn more at prestarpackaging.com. about creative carding. creative carding is the gift card packaging division of prestar packaging, inc, a family owned and operated rigid set-up box manufacturing company. that sparked an idea and thus the new design for the world's first one-piece unitary gift card box was invented. we also have the most dedicated and caring family of employees of any company in the world.

generated_description: creative carding is a gift card packaging division of prestar packaging, inc, located in christiansburg, virginia. the company specializes in manufacturing patented gift card boxes, gift card folders, and accessories made from recycled materials. creative carding offers a wide variety of colors, patterns, and textures, with full customization options available. all products are 100% recyclable and made from 80% post-consumer paper products. the company is known for its innovative designs, including the world's first one-piece unitary gift card box, which received a patent in 2007. creative carding operates alongside prestar packaging, inc, which is the largest manufacturer of gift card packaging in the u.s., shipping its products to 17 countries globally.
